<i><font size=+2>Oophaga speciosa</font></i> <font color=grey>(Schmidt, 1857)</font>
<br>
Splendid Poison Frog</td><td align=right valign=top><small>family: <a href="/lists/Dendrobatidae.shtml">Dendrobatidae</a></small><br><small>subfamily: <a href=https://amphibiaweb.org/cgi/amphib_query?max=200&orderbyaw=Genus%2Bspecies&include_synonymies=Yes&show_photos=Yes&rel-subfamily=equals&where-subfamily=Dendrobatinae>Dendrobatinae</a></small><br><small>genus: <a href=https://amphibiaweb.org/cgi/amphib_query?max=200&orderbyaw=Genus%2Bspecies&include_synonymies=Yes&show_photos=Yes&rel-genus=equals&where-genus=Oophaga>Oophaga</a></small><br>
